list.abstract: 《complicated》是加拿大女歌手艾薇儿·拉维尼演唱的一首流行音乐歌曲，于2002年9月3日由索尼音乐唱片公司发行，后被收录在艾薇儿·拉维尼的首张录音室专辑《Let Go》中。 该歌曲曾获得爱尔兰、澳洲等国家的音乐排行榜冠军、日本MTV音乐录影带奖“最佳新人录像”奖、朱诺奖年度最佳单曲等荣誉。
《Complicated》是由比利时电音组合Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike与法国天王级制作人大卫·库塔（David Guetta）合作制作，美国歌手Kiiara演唱的一首歌曲，于2017年7月28日发布。

yingyinNormal.en: I guess you can say my family's complicated the way that most families are complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可能会说我家庭很复杂，其实很多家庭都很复杂的。

yingyinNormal.en: Exactly. But it's tricky. I've never seen a more complicated potion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没有错。这药很难做，我从来没见过这么复杂的配方。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I just, I don't want to get in the middle of something so complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想介入这么复杂的事。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, complicated moral situation? No right, No wrong? You have to tell David.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道的，复杂的道德情况，是没有错或对。你必须要告诉大卫。

yingyinNormal.en: As it stands, Ethan Hunt is a man without a country. This makes killing him decidedly less complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且现在，伊森·亨特是一个无国籍人士，所以杀了他不会牵扯到什么复杂的事情。

yingyinNormal.en: He will not know how to operate it! It is very complicated. Heavy on one end, light on the other. Shush!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不会知道怎么控制这个的！很复杂的，一头重，一头轻。安静！

yingyinNormal.en: Mm, it's complicated. But as I remember it, the essentials are get chosen last, get hit by the ball, cry, go home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 规则很复杂的，不过在我看来，棒球的精髓就是最后才被选中，被球打，痛哭，回家。

yingyinNormal.en: He was relaxed and loose and calm. Well, Sheldon's a complicated man. He said "Whatev." Give him a brain scan that might be a tumor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿是个复杂的男人。他很放松而且散漫且平静。他说了"无所"。带他去做大脑扫描可能长瘤了。

yingyinNormal.en: They're independent markets. They're not always correlated. I know it sounds odd, but these are very complicated products. They are correlated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们属于独立市场，并不是总是相关的，我知道这听起来很奇怪，但这本来就是非常复杂的产品。它们是互相关联的。

yingyinNormal.en: One day he asked a woman who was there how it was going, how did you like the Facebook, She answered with a long and pretty complicated sentence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一天他问一位女性，问她觉得Facebook怎么样，她用一个很长很复杂的句子进行了回答。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Go to the police, they're really excellent at dealing with this complicated sort of stuff. Tell them I sent you that ought to get a reaction. Night-night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 去找警察吧，他们很擅长，对付这些复杂的案子。跟他们说我让你来的，这样能引起重视，晚安。

yingyinNormal.en: Girlfriend-eses? It's complicated. You know what's not complicated? Zay. Available.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女朋友们？这事有点复杂。你们知道什么不复杂吗？小赛，还单身。

yingyinNormal.en: It's more complicated than that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 实际情况远比嘴上说得复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: He has a complicated response to authority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他对官僚的态度很复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: But the problem, this game is really complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 问题是，这项游戏真的很复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: Great. So where do I find you? Well, it's complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧那我去哪里找你们？噢，这有点复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: They're not as complicated as yours. They are very simple.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们不像你的那么复杂，它们极简单。

yingyinNormal.en: Caine is complicated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 凯恩他身世很复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: Like I said, complicated game. So did I win or not?
yingyinNormal.zh: 正如我说的，这个游戏很复杂。那我到底赢没赢？

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know. It's so complicated. I work with this guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，真是太复杂了，这男的是我同事耶。
